title: Interstellar - Quantifiable connection (Piano Cover)
description:
Hello there,
So I really love this unreleased piece of music from the movie Interstellar. It is when Cooper, trapped in the 5th dimension, finds out that he brought himself to Nasa to begin the mission, and transmit the data from the blackhole to Murph via morse code in the watch. Very good moment and the music is so pretty and full of hope.
I worked hard during the last week to make an arrangment since I can't find any already existing. I am happy with it and hope you like it too. Since it is the main theme over and over again during 4min, it was hard to manage to make it sound a bit different every time and make it sound as though there is a progression happening. I hope I did not fail to that.
I hope you like it!
